te><br />\n啱啊 迫人俾錢知唔知醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919a9622d53e8fa1b9686c9fdf5a5cd56409b622","tid":230821,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:45:59.000Z","msg":"我代你去啦，可以幫你比全數<br />\nPm"},{"pid":"9e86fc8ec9eaa30cd1eb5c0a6f75cc16bc3cab65","tid":230821,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我代你去啦，可以幫你比全數<br />\nPm</blockquote><br />\n唔係我黎 你去名校Secret搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b7f25de74d6360b7107f39f1c544a16a093909","tid":230821,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"謝師宴應該係放榜先搞<br />\n未出成績，點解要多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caeacc03f06f5abacb623a026de3324c02bf4bd3","tid":230821,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝師宴應該係放榜先搞<br />\n未出成績，點解要多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放榜前搞係要話俾學生知，<br />\n學生成績好唔好其實唔撚關老師事，<br />\n但老師又想enjoy吓班細嘅當自己老竇老母咁錫<br />\n成個傻仔咁，<br />\n咁咪去囉反正又唔洗錢"},{"pid":"14b6da8717646739b5ca07f239526e7513aef15e","tid":230821,"uid":65142,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"留言個嗰話學生冇份出糧俾老師呢個point都冇撚腦<br />\n老師的確係個個月幾皮野落袋唔係做義工喎屌<br />\n關邊個出糧乜撚野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難為咁多傻鳩like 咁又做左所謂既神回"},{"pid":"67758a256e90996b97d89fdc493d6b6c8af67feb","tid":230821,"uid":30901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:11:28.000Z","msg":"講起謝師宴真係火都黎撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食乜撚野可以食到$1500啊<br />\n你話有女𥄫都好 仆你個街 半級女仔都係蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外嗰一半 仲有