own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你老母垃圾教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲衰過數學MC撞曬C<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88af26694a12b8e664baab4c61ff7207d6dd8f1","tid":230821,"uid":4453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:18:36.000Z","msg":"先唔講應唔應該請<br />\n個Comment 都幾冇point 下<br />\n首先假定d老師好俾之機教同學生好想要本grad book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要話學生冇直接俾過錢老師所以要請，而家問題係d老師有收過錢吖嘛，仲要薪高糧準<br />\n有樣嘢叫公民福利<br />\n去睇急症嗰一百夠唔係直接俾d醫生護士啦，唔見你出院請全醫院食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n況且呢個福利唔係白攞，d學生父母要交税，學生grad左做野又要交"},{"pid":"d2b4627a5833a1e0ebf223709979098ec16d83c1","tid":230821,"uid":33422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:19:21.000Z","msg":"其實你走數班搞手都吹你唔漲<br />\n<br />\n利申俾班主任打電話上屋企追數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老母話俾返錢會留個好印象俾學校，retake 都有學校收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab42a4470cadbc942ff514824e4695a9dec1ff7","tid":230821,"uid":21391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"我間垃圾學校 講明要交謝師宴錢先可以拎畢業證書"},{"pid":"ef4f0ae0d99ebbd9da2fe02848a121b370fd1c72","tid":230821,"uid":30214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:25:02.000Z","msg":"當年走數但照去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c6d4a0454ed6ee34a6eeba8fe37960ebc941c1","tid":230821,"uid":30901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"