書<br />\n鳩吹唔見咗HR都唔會問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb9b38e08d3dae22bcdc366ef2698ea60f5eeb9","tid":230821,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"冇去gradin<br />\n比咗300幾 覺得冇咩所謂<br />\ngradbook都冇攞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nnone of my business"},{"pid":"78f08444352119467258b204ead7e5a9a6358f6f","tid":230821,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我間垃圾學校 講明要交謝師宴錢先可以拎畢業證書</blockquote><br />\n我嗰陣d搞手都係咁講<br />\n我心諗到時U grad邊有人理中學畢業證書<br />\n鳩吹唔見咗HR都唔會問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好似都冇攞到張畢業證書 <br />\n癈事返去攞 覺得中學姐都冇乜所謂 有乜好證明"},{"pid":"f5f36a77c17f28d33d6b407f17ef2c79a2facb19","tid":230821,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:39:30.000Z","msg":"Gradbook過幾年就會覺得好阻定 何況十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55521d2acaefe624ca67b8206d37eb9371eae64e","tid":230821,"uid":9957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gradbook過幾年就會覺得好阻定 何況十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n特别覺得都唔會再contact班中同<br />\n入到u又另一班人啦<br />\n你話到時同科又同行咪keep contact<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb7c1069976092c4fff406fc5abdfb95f8e6856","tid":230821,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我間垃圾學校 講明要交謝師宴錢先可以拎畢業證書</blockquote><br />\n我嗰陣d搞手都係咁講<br />\n我心諗到時U grad邊有人理中學畢業證書<br />\n鳩吹唔見咗HR都唔會問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好似都冇攞到張畢業證書 <br />\n癈事返去攞 覺得中學姐都冇乜所謂 有乜好證明</blockquote><br />\nAgger 名校就話可以打下飛機姐<br />\n但最top嘅名校學生通常歸屬感好強，多數都會去<br />\nBtw佢地邊有咁大權力，最後咪