:4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"比啦垃圾中學雞 <br />\n出黎社會做野工作 仲多唔請願既夾錢野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩冇人迫到 笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a29b0ff9eb5daed63e37bdbf7ab4e496c24cd7","tid":230821,"uid":44775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:54:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你走數班搞手都吹你唔漲<br />\n<br />\n利申俾<span style=\"color: red;\">班主任打電話上屋企追數</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老母話俾返錢會留個好印象俾學校，retake 都有學校收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba27a91eac146b8e75115e368af8c92b65adff6","tid":230821,"uid":55594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今時今日，唔去謝師宴<br />\n都要你俾錢/俾一半錢 <br />\n你地覺得係咪應份？<br />\n<br />\n應份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話曬老師教足你六年 點都要請佢食<br />\n<br />\n唔應份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾教畜 白攞人工 請你老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/232907_87557aa4040483d0b8059b3124520fb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F232907_87557aa4040483d0b8059b3124520fb8.jpg&h=80bb1092&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n根據winnie fung 邏輯，<br />\n學生應該多謝納稅人而唔係有比足糧既老師</blockquote><br />\n條囡被人圍完唔識搏就係自己page 企道德高地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o2t1s708\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo2t1s708&h=efa5665c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔去謝師宴等如無禮貌唔感謝老師<br />\n又咪比你班搞手攞彩扮一晚大人<br />\n表達感謝洗撚去大酒店搞場大龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f578c367aee89254ec6e00e98931eb03f5c0227","tid":230821,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>謝師宴應該係放榜先搞<br />\n未出成績，點解要多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放榜前搞係要話俾學生知，<br />\n學生成績好唔好其實唔撚關老師事，<br />\n但老師又想enjoy吓班細嘅當自己老竇老母咁錫<br />\n成個傻仔咁，<br />\n咁咪去囉反正又唔洗錢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eedfbee030e2a8b762882cede85bde1738a846c","tid":230821,"uid":7262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講起謝師宴真係火都黎撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食乜撚野可以食到$1500啊<br />\n你話有女𥄫都好 仆你個街 半級女仔都係蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外嗰一半 仲有啲係肥西 𥄫條撚咩<br />\n班垃圾教畜完全冇教過書 <br />\n我喺英文堂聽過既Skill就係<br />\n如果你唔識做TFNG嗰類題型既話 就全部填晒NG啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你老母垃圾教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩 你咁撚戇鳩 <br />\n1500$去謝師宴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拎去同屋企人食左佢好過啦"},{"pid":"1823cb5529d1ed94dab7343d533c35ec7231a79e","tid":230821,"uid":63740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"留言個位on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話個個老師都唔認真教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係教我個啲上堂特別鍾意吹水<br />\n教bio個位先經典每次上堂至小遲10分鐘<br />\n跟住上堂就拎半堂泥講自己啲家事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比佢教咗兩年都係咁撚樣<br />\nunun腳一個月袋幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果比佢搞到要出去補習<br />\n係咪好應該佢回水比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n謝師宴比錢冇問題,但係比錢請埋依啲撚樣食飯條氣點都會唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：除咗bio科科都冇補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9121bb86498bb48e902eaf72a970dde12d1e87d2","tid":230821,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講起謝師宴真係火都黎撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食乜撚野可以食到$1500啊<br />\n你話有女𥄫都好 仆你個街 半級女仔都係蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外嗰一半 仲有啲係肥西 𥄫條撚咩<br />\n班垃圾教畜完全冇教過書 <br />\n我喺英文堂聽過既Skill就係<br />\n如果你唔識做TFNG嗰類題型既話 就全部填晒NG啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  屌你老母垃圾教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嘩 你咁撚戇鳩 <br />\n1500$去謝師宴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拎去同屋企人食左佢好過啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句真<br />\n請阿爸阿媽唔好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccba4af880e231017064f84b11228271ef5e43ff","tid":230821,"uid":110135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今時今日，唔去謝師宴<br />\n都要你俾錢/俾一半錢 <br />\n你地覺得係咪應